---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Financial Advisor Marketing Automation in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/professional-services/financial-advisors" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Financial Advisors
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Financial Advisors</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">10 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Financial Advisor Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Build your book of business, nurture prospects through long sales cycles, and generate quality referrals automatically.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Financial advisory is a relationship business with long sales cycles. Automation keeps you top-of-mind during months of consideration while you focus on serving clients.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Long-Term Prospect Nurturing</h2>

          <p>
            Prospects often need 6-18 months before they're ready to move forward. Automated educational sequences—retirement tips, market insights, planning strategies—build trust and keep you top-of-mind until they're ready.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Client Retention</h2>

          <p>
            Clients who feel neglected drift to competitors. Regular touchpoints—quarterly review reminders, birthday greetings, market updates—demonstrate ongoing value and strengthen relationships.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Systematic Referrals</h2>

          <p>
            Your best clients will refer—if you ask. Automated referral requests at optimal moments (after positive reviews, anniversaries, milestones) generate consistent introductions to qualified prospects.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your Practice?</h3>
            <p class="text-emerald-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd automate prospect nurturing for your financial advisory.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-emerald-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
